title: The 2019 NFL Draft Roundup | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
The winners and losers from the draft, the Josh Rosen trade, the GMs who separated themselves from the rest, the players that went too high, the best value picks, and more.
Host: Robert Mays, Kevin Clark
Guest: Danny Kelly
